public static interface Trace.CuramMethodInvocationHandler
extends java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler

CuramMethodInvocationHandler is an interface that must be implemented by all method trace handlers. A method trace handler is the class responsible for wrapping all method invocations with trace information. CuramMethodInvocationHandlerDefault is the default class provided by Curam as a method trace handler.
